334
00:14:45,151 --> 00:14:47,887 line:-1
about the most important things
shown in photos --


335
00:14:47,887 --> 00:14:49,722 line:-1
may accompany photos.


336
00:14:49,722 --> 00:14:53,092 line:-1
So to create great and
inclusive photos experiences,


337
00:14:53.092 --> 00:14:56.462 line:-1 position:50%
