346
00:15:18,751 --> 00:15:21,154 line:-1
But there are a lot of photos
out there


347
00:15:21.154 --> 00:15:24.090 line:-1 position:50%
and many of them
do not have descriptions.


348
00:15:24.090 --> 00:15:26.526 line:-1 position:50%
Machine learning is
a tool that can help.


349
00:15:26.526 --> 00:15:30.196 line:-1 position:50%
A machine-learning-trained model
can generate image descriptions


350
00:15:30,196 --> 00:15:33,599 line:-1
automatically, quickly,
and at scale.


351
00:15:33.599 --> 00:15:35.701 line:-1 position:50%
So our team trained a model


352
00:15:35,701 --> 00:15:39,438 line:-1
to generate detailed natural
language descriptions of images


353
00:15:39.438 --> 00:15:42.208 line:-1 position:50%
across iOS, which we call


354
00:15:42.208 --> 00:15:45.278 line:-1 position:50%
VoiceOver Recognition
image descriptions.


355
00:15:45,278 --> 00:15:48,114 line:-1
Let’s listen to the VoiceOver
Recognition image description


356
00:15:48,114 --> 00:15:50,016 line:-1
of this photo.


357
00:15:50,016 --> 00:15:54,053 line:-1
>> VoiceOver: A giraffe standing
