367
00:16:20.213 --> 00:16:22.114 line:-1 position:50%
whether you’re working
on your own


368
00:16:22.114 --> 00:16:24.150 line:-1 position:50%
or at a large company.


369
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:26,219 line:-1
Keep those diversity axes
in mind


370
00:16:26.219 --> 00:16:29.689 line:-1 position:50%
when thinking about what groups
you should prioritize.


371
00:16:29.689 --> 00:16:32.291 line:-1 position:50%
One aspect of machine learning
representation


372
00:16:32,291 --> 00:16:34,660 line:-1
that our team learned more about


373
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:37,697 line:-1
was how people’s gender
