or low vision?


384
00:17:07.193 --> 00:17:09.795 line:-1 position:50%
Well, people who are blind
or low vision


385
00:17:09,795 --> 00:17:12,198 line:-1
have all sorts
of gender identities.


386
00:17:12,198 --> 00:17:13,432 line:-1
In other words,


387
00:17:13.432 --> 00:17:15.568 line:-1 position:50%
these characteristics
will work together


388
00:17:15.568 --> 00:17:18.170 line:-1 position:50%
to impact the experiences
people have


389
00:17:18,170 --> 00:17:21,040 line:-1
while reading
image descriptions.


390
00:17:21,040 --> 00:17:22,875 line:-1
Intersectionality was developed


391
00:17:22.875 --> 00:17:26.579 line:-1 position:50%
by legal and critical race
scholar Kimberlé Crenshaw.


392
00:17:26.579 --> 00:17:28.915 line:-1 position:50%
It recognizes
the unique experiences


393
00:17:28,915 --> 00:17:31,951 line:-1
and needs of people
who have multiple identities


394
00:17:31,951 --> 00:17:34,353 line:-1
which are systematically
disadvantaged.


395
00:17:34.353 --> 00:17:38.157 line:-1 position:50%
In this example, listening
to intersectional perspectives


396
00:17:38.157 --> 00:17:41.394 line:-1 position:50%
helped us to develop
great experiences


397
00:17:41,394 --> 00:17:44,163 line:-1
for people with identities
across groups


398
00:17:44,163 --> 00:17:46,232 line:-1
in the diversity axes.


399
00:17:46,232 --> 00:17:49,835 line:-1
Specifically, intersectionality
helped us listen to people


400
00:17:49.835 --> 00:17:53.039 line:-1 position:50%
tell us how being both blind
or low vision


401
00:17:53.039 --> 00:17:57.343 line:-1 position:50%
and being a minority gender,
like non-binary and transgender,


402
00:17:57,343 --> 00:17:59,545 line:-1
together impacted
their experiences


403
00:17:59.545 --> 00:18:02.048 line:-1 position:50%
reading image descriptions.


404
00:18:02,048 --> 00:18:04,383 line:-1
To ensure that we learned
perspectives


405
00:18:04.383 --> 00:18:08.187 line:-1 position:50%
from people who live at
this very specific intersection,


406
00:18:08.187 --> 00:18:11.557 line:-1 position:50%
our team partnered
