498
00:22:34,253 --> 00:22:36,822 line:-1
It may mean you need
to make hard calls


499
00:22:36.822 --> 00:22:39.291 line:-1 position:50%
by cutting back
the release of one feature


500
00:22:39,291 --> 00:22:43,295 line:-1
so you can make fewer features
