516
00:23:24,370 --> 00:23:27,273 line:-1
Learning how to do better
and how we can do more


517
00:23:27,273 --> 00:23:30,109 line:-1
is part
of the inclusive journey.


518
00:23:30,109 --> 00:23:33,245 line:-1
You can also remember
to continue to reevaluate,


519
00:23:33.245 --> 00:23:36.315 line:-1 position:50%
strengthen, and grow
with real-life developments,


520
00:23:36,315 --> 00:23:38,183 line:-1
or as you learn more
about the ways


521
00:23:38,183 --> 00:23:40,919 line:-1
you can make the experience
better for people.


522
00:23:40.919 --> 00:23:45.391 line:-1 position:50%
It also means not just moving on
