571
00:26:06,965 --> 00:26:09,802 line:-1
To help people relive
moments they care about,


572
00:26:09.802 --> 00:26:10.836 line:-1 position:50%
we had to embrace


573
00:26:10,836 --> 00:26:14,940 line:-1
the breadth of life experiences
