577
00:26:23.982 --> 00:26:25.083 line:-1 position:50%
in different time zones


578
00:26:25,083 --> 00:26:27,719 line:-1
to allow more people
to participate.


579
00:26:27.719 --> 00:26:29.788 line:-1 position:50%
Large groups tend
to be intimidating,


580
00:26:29,788 --> 00:26:32,858 line:-1
and you can miss out
on great suggestions.


581
00:26:32,858 --> 00:26:34,793 line:-1
Once we gathered
new memories ideas,


582
00:26:34,793 --> 00:26:36,195 line:-1
we analyzed each one


583
00:26:36.195 --> 00:26:38.897 line:-1 position:50%
through the lenses
of the diversity axes.


584
00:26:38,897 --> 00:26:41,567 line:0
