588
00:26:52,578 --> 00:26:55,747 line:-1
Who are we building this for?
Who are excluding?


589
00:26:55.747 --> 00:26:57.816 line:-1 position:50%
And how will people feel?


590
00:26:57,816 --> 00:26:59,518 line:-1
This exercise helped us select


591
00:26:59,518 --> 00:27:01,687 line:-1
