613
00:28:07.252 --> 00:28:09.888 line:-1 position:50%
Being mindful of difficult
life experiences,


614
00:28:09.888 --> 00:28:12.591 line:-1 position:50%
and design with sensitivity.


615
00:28:12.591 --> 00:28:16.695 line:-1 position:50%
To achieve this objective,
we used another technique.


616
00:28:16.695 --> 00:28:19.798 line:-1 position:50%
While brainstorming meetings
are great at producing ideas


617
00:28:19.798 --> 00:28:21.733 line:-1 position:50%
and increasing creativity,


618
00:28:21,733 --> 00:28:24,903 line:-1
specific topics require
extra sensitivity


619
00:28:24.903 --> 00:28:27.439 line:-1 position:50%
and your undivided attention.


620
00:28:27.439 --> 00:28:29.908 line:-1 position:50%
So we leaned towards
individual interviews


621
00:28:29,908 --> 00:28:32,044 line:-1
to dive deeper
and provide a safe space


622
00:28:32,044 --> 00:28:34,379 line:-1
for people to share
their stories.


623
00:28:34,379 --> 00:28:37,349 line:-1
I encourage you to give it a try
and schedule conversations


624
00:28:37.349 --> 00:28:39.484 line:-1 position:50%
with people who had concerns
with your app


625
00:28:39.484 --> 00:28:41.219 line:-1 position:50%
and didn't feel included.


626
00:28:41.219 --> 00:28:43.755 line:-1 position:50%
For Memories,
we hosted several conversations


627
00:28:43.755 --> 00:28:48.327 line:-1 position:50%
to unpack the feedback gathered
during our preliminary research.


628
00:28:48.327 --> 00:28:51.863 line:-1 position:50%
Several people shared that they
enjoyed revisiting their photos,


629
00:28:51.863 --> 00:28:54.066 line:-1 position:50%
except when they featured
a person


630
00:28:54.066 --> 00:28:56.435 line:-1 position:50%
they'd rather not
be reminded of.


631
00:28:56.435 --> 00:28:59.871 line:-1 position:50%
Before designing solutions,
we carved space to empathize,


632
00:28:59.871 --> 00:29:03.175 line:-1 position:50%
listen, and understand
their perspectives.


633
00:29:03,175 --> 00:29:06,445 line:-1
We gently unpacked the what,
how, when,


634
00:29:06.445 --> 00:29:08.714 line:-1 position:50%
and especially the why.


635
00:29:08,714 --> 00:29:13,185 line:-1
We were interested in what made
a memory enjoyable or not,


636
00:29:13,185 --> 00:29:15,887 line:-1
